{"tid":2495673,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［何謂投資］用巴菲特角度同你解釋點解唔好買樓同bitcoin黎炒","createTime":"2021-04-19T10:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T10:24:34.000Z","uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"278f5dd0a93e8c97d3b29fa07d72d3a367ac7f21","tid":2495673,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:19:16.000Z","msg":"何謂投資？<br />\n巴菲特認為投資係你買一樣野，即係所謂資產<br />\n而呢樣資產可以幫到你<span class=\"red\">生產價值</span><br />\n咁先係叫投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁何謂生產到價值？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PxA7sH5ZqLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPxA7sH5ZqLA&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=076045ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PxA7sH5ZqLA</a><br />\n<br />\n片入面佢舉左一個例子，例如你買左一塊田，咁塊田背後你用黎種菜，咁佢可以為你帶黎額外收入，除左呢個額外收入，你仲擁有左一塊田<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而樓同bitcoin本身無帶有生產價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你買樓同bitcoin嘅原因都係因為想搵到下一個人願意出更高嘅價錢同你買左佢<br />\n<br />\n簡單d黎講就係接火棒遊戲，如果無人肯接火棒，本身呢個資產又無生產價值，咁到最後個結局就係會仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n套用現實，到底宜家買唔買樓同bitcoin好？<br />\n<br />\n先講樓<br />\n<br />\n如果宜家仲買樓係唸住有下一個原因同你接火棒，咁一定<br />\n係一個好錯誤嘅選擇<br />\n接火棒最主要因素就係從demand同supply去考慮<br />\n樓未來demand趨向平穩，而supply就越黎越多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可能會話，依，唔係波，樓價好似唔識跌仲升緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁一定架喇，呢個叫做<span class=\"red\">物價通脹</span>而非叫價值提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除非你蠢到連債券 股票都唔識買，咁買樓收租可能都係一個唔錯選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁bitcoin呢？呢點你就要唸未來多唔多人同你接火棒喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次講到呢到先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a36399440f2617232d5b64810263a228c1172c","tid":2495673,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"bitcoin is a scam<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ea6da3520016f9bdba70216fa22ae6855a912b","tid":2495673,"uid":316667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"7a02bcc61a501df10fbd4b6c8d1aa8e93e613841","tid":2495673,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13ea6da3520016f9bdba70216fa22ae6855a912b","tid":2495673,"uid":316667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"On9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"on9都有錢過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a